                        "What Is a Modern POS System?",
                        "A modern POS system is a cloud-connected platform that combines billing, inventory tracking, customer data, and reporting in one interface. It runs on desktops, tablets, and mobile devices so staff can ring up sales anywhere on the floor. The best POS systems also integrate with accounting, e-commerce, and ERP systems to avoid duplicate data entry.",
