                        "Electronics and Hardware: Serial number tracking and warranty-based returns handling.",
                        "Why Choose Primatech Solutions for POS Development",
                        "Custom Workflows: We align the POS with your existing billing and inventory process.",
                        "Fast Deployment: Rapid setup with data migration and staff onboarding support.",
                        "Hardware Friendly: Compatible with barcode scanners, printers, cash drawers, and tablets.",
                        "ERP Ready: Built to connect with accounting, procurement, and CRM from day one.",
